 165:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****     (#) There are two modes of transfer:
 166:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****        (++) Blocking mode : The communication is performed in the polling mode.
 167:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****             The status of all data processing is returned by the same function
 168:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****             after finishing transfer.
 169:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****        (++) No-Blocking mode : The communication is performed using Interrupts
 170:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****             or DMA. These functions return the status of the transfer startup.
 171:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****             The end of the data processing will be indicated through the
 172:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****             dedicated I2S IRQ when using Interrupt mode or the DMA IRQ when
 173:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****             using DMA mode.
 174:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c **** 
 175:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****     (#) Blocking mode functions are :
 176:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****         (++) HAL_I2SEx_TransmitReceive()
 177:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c **** 
 178:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****     (#) No-Blocking mode functions with Interrupt are :
 179:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****         (++) HAL_I2SEx_TransmitReceive_IT()
 180:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****         (++) HAL_I2SEx_FullDuplex_IRQHandler()
 181:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c **** 
 182:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****     (#) No-Blocking mode functions with DMA are :
 183:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****         (++) HAL_I2SEx_TransmitReceive_DMA()
 184:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c **** 
 185:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****     (#) A set of Transfer Complete Callback are provided in non Blocking mode:
 186:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c ****         (++) HAL_I2SEx_TxRxCpltCallback()
 187:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2s_ex.c **** @endverbatim
